<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٩٩٠ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا قَبِيصَةُ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ، عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ دِينَارٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ ابْنِ عُمَرَ <span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">سَمِعْتُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">(الْفِتْنَةُ مِنْ هَا هُنَا)</span> وَأَشَارَ إِلَى الْمَشْرِقِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
